    public abstract class AbstractWaitForCentralPeakAgentRegistrationBehaviour
extends jade.core.behaviours.SimpleBehaviour
implements de.enflexit.jade.phonebook.PhoneBookListener
    The Class AbstractWaitForCentralPeakAgentRegistrationBehaviour can be extended and used to wait for the registration of the central PEAK agents, specified by the corresponding PeakPhoneBookEntry.PeakRole.
